## Data Asset Licenses (not covered by the MIT license above)

The bundled data assets retain their original licenses and attribution. The MIT
license above applies to the project's source code only.

- **NASA Blue Marble NG** texture (`public/assets/earth/blue-marble-*.jpg`) —
  NASA imagery, public domain. Credit: NASA Earth Observatory.
- **ETOPO1** heightmap / normal map (`public/assets/earth/etopo1-*.png`) —
  NOAA NCEI, public domain. Credit: NOAA National Centers for Environmental
  Information.
- **Natural Earth** boundaries & labels (`public/assets/boundaries/`,
  `public/assets/labels/`) — public domain. Credit: Natural Earth
  (naturalearthdata.com).
- **ERA5 10m wind** frames (`public/data/era5/`) — produced by ECMWF /
  Copernicus Climate Change Service (C3S), accessed via ARCO-ERA5 on Google
  Cloud Public Datasets. Contains modified Copernicus Climate Change Service
  information [2024]. Neither the European Commission nor ECMWF is responsible
  for any use of the downstream products. See `docs/ERA5-DATA-PROVENANCE.md`
  for the full citation.
